// alice_relay — Alice Map Alcove.
//
// Built as part of intro-v1 Task 04 ("Under-town cartography route").
// Sits east of `under_town_pipes`, same row in the gridvania view,
// so the path from drain → under-town → Alice reads as a coherent
// eastward private route.
//
// Function: Alice gives the sealed route note and frames map
// knowledge as something that can be protected or exposed. The room
// is a small alcove with one warm NPC, a few labels naming the
// progression beat, and a sealed private door whose label promises
// it opens after Bob's field survey.
//
// Width 1024 keeps the world-row tidy. Height 768 matches
// under_town_pipes for a clean side-scroll transition.
//
// Transitions:
// - Left-edge EdgeExit `alice_from_under_town` ← under_town_pipes/under_town_to_alice
// - Right-edge EdgeExit `alice_to_bob` → bob_relay/bob_from_alice
// - Private return door (Task 08 wires it): currently a LockWall +
//   label "MAP_SECRET: opens after Bob survey". Forward-declared so
//   Task 08 can promote it to a real LoadingZone without rebuilding
//   the alcove.
//
// Layout (1024×768):
//
//   +---------------------------------------------------+
//   | ▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒ ceiling ▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒  |
//   |                                                   |
//   |   [Alice]                                         |  Alice alcove
//   |   ←from pipes                          → to Bob  |
//   |   ▒▒▒▒▒▒    P2: Sealed Route Note                 |
//   |   ▒▒▒▒▒▒    Reward: Private Map Marks             |
//   |             [private return — sealed]             |  LockWall placeholder
//   |▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒ floor ▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒  |
//   +---------------------------------------------------+

